results.raw_content:
Dongguan Dongsong Electronic Co.,Ltd.
Dongguan Dongsong Electronic Co., Ltd (DYS) was established in East District of Dongguan City in 2000. 18 years of expertise has enabled DYS to become a high-quality server of Switching Mode Power Supply(SMPS), and has been recognized as a National High-tech Enterprise. Our Main Products includes: Switching power adapter, Charger, LED Driver, Type-C Adapter, Open Frame Power Supply, Industrial Power Supply, which has been widely used in the Fields of Computer Peripherals & Communication(IT) Devices , Audio & Video Apparatus, Toys Consumer Electronics, Household Appliances, Medical & Healthcare Instruments, Industrial & Military Equipment, etc.
DYS is configured with rich resources for production equipment and management system. We own several modern functional factories which cover over than 20,000 square meters. With more than 1,000 staff, our production capability reaches up to 2,500kpcs per month. In addition, Factory has been approved by Quality Management System ISO9001 and environment management system ISO14001. With the expansion and improvement of customers, DYS has gradually introduced automation, digitalization and information technology to meet demands of modernized production on the basis of the existing systematization and process, which makes DYS upgrade into a smart enterprise in the near future. DYS strictly fulfills her corporate social responsibility and obligation to care for her employees and continues to promote product upgrades to meet the classes of environment protection and low-carbon production during all procedures.
DYS attaches great importance to product safety and quality, and strives for perfection throughout all stages from product design to manufacturing. ‘safety Parts, Safety Guaranty’ is regarded as the main concept of our company. The factory has equipped with professional safety and quality test laboratories, including: EMC, ESD, surge test, temperature rise test, cold and hot shock test, salt spray test, drop test, swing test, vibration test and RoHs test labs. Besides, we have long-term cooperation with international authority agencies such as TUV, UL, SGS, BV, and ITS to ensure that DYS power units can withstand the most stringent safety and quality inspections, while all our products meet efficiency level VI requirement, and have obtained CB, UL, CUL, ETL, CETL, FCC, CE, GS, BS, SAA, PSE, CCC, KC, EAC, PSB, BSMI, TISI, ST, SIRIM, TECT, SABS, SASO, NOM, S-Mark, BIS, ErP, CEC, DOE, NrCan, GEMS, MEPS, RoHs, Reach, PAHs, etc.
DYS has a skillful and experienced R&D team with more than 50 engineers, which always keeps upgrading products to meet market expansion. We persist the concept of high quality standard to continuously create value for human beings and the earth. Our products power ranges from 5W to 600W, which can satisfy all products in various fields, DYS also specializes in customizing exclusive power solutions for her customers. Because of over 18 years’ unremitting efforts and pursuit on specialization by DYS group, Our Brand is famous both at home and abroad.
Sincerely thank you for cooperating with DYS, We will strive our best to serve you and support the growth of your business. You are warmly welcomed to our factory for a visit and we look forward to a fruitful and long-term cooperation!

Company Introduction
Operating since 2000
Dongsong Electronic was founded in 2000 in the east district of Dongguan City, Guangdong, China. We are a professional switching power supply manufacturer, integrating R&D, mass production, sales and services under one roof. Backed by our 15,000-square-meter factory and 800 staff members, we are able to complete all orders excellently and on time.
Wide Range of Products to Choose from
We are an experienced company dealing with different products. Our products range includes:
Audio power supplies have power range from three to 150W and all comply with the level VI of energy efficiency. We have more than 15 years' experience goes in audio power adapters. Now Beats, Philips, Denon, B&O, Braven, Jawbone, Pioneer, Polk, Boston are equipped with our adapters.
IT power supplies have power range from three to 150W and all comply with the level VI of energy efficiency. They are applied on information devices, telecommunication devices, set-top box and mobile phone chargers.
Open-frame power supplies have power range from 24 to 300W and all can pass EMC
Multi-port USB chargers obtained global agency approvals including CB, ETL, CE, C-TICK, RCM, packed with changeable AC plug or AC cord.
LED driver have power range from five to 150W and have dimmable mode, constant voltage mode and constant current mode.
Excelling in American, European and Australian Markets
We have been developing and enjoying prominent sales growth particularly in the American, European and Australian markets - emerging as one of the best power supply manufacturers over the years.
Meeting Various Quality Requirements and Standard
Our products are widely used in audio, video, mobile phones, computers, digital cameras, CCTV cameras, MP3/MP4 players, LCD monitors and telecommunication equipment. And because of our meticulousness, they meet UL/cUL, ETL/CETL, FCC, GS, CE, SAA, C-Tick/RCM, CCC, PSE, KC, Argentina S-Mark, PSB, BSMI, NOM, C-Tick, VCCI, TISI, EAC, SASO, KUCAS, SABS, SII, CEC, ERP, MEPS, RoHS, REACH and PAHs requirements.

results.content: BAE Systems, Inc. is the U.S. subsidiary of BAE Systems plc, a global defense, security and aerospace company which delivers a full range of products and services for air, land and naval forces, as well as advanced electronics, security, information technology solutions and customer support services.

BAE Systems, Inc.
Electronic Systems produces commercial and defense electronics for flight and engine control, electronic warfare, surveillance, communications, and power and energy management.
Intelligence & Security delivers a broad range of solutions and services enabling militaries and governments to successfully carry out their missions. The company provides large-scale systems engineering, integration, and sustainment services across air, land, sea, space, and cyber domains.
Platforms & Services is a leading provider of tracked and wheeled armored combat vehicles, naval guns, naval ship repair and modernization, artillery and missile launching systems, advanced precision strike munitions and ordnance, and other technologies for U.S. and international customers.
Headquartered in Falls Church, Virginia, BAE Systems, Inc. in the United States, United Kingdom, and Sweden, provides support and service solutions for current and future defense, intelligence, and civilian systems; designs, develops and manufactures a wide range of electronic systems and subsystems for both military and commercial applications; produces specialized security and protection products; and designs, develops, produces, and provides service support of armored combat vehicles, artillery systems, and munitions.
BAE Systems, Inc. is a Delaware corporation that has mitigated our foreign ownership through a Special Security Agreement between the U.S. Government, BAE Systems, Inc. and BAE Systems plc. That agreement calls for the appointment of outside directors who, in conjunction with other U.S. based board members, comprise a Government Security Committee. The Government Security Committee has the responsibility for overseeing the company’s compliance with U.S. Government Security and Export regulations, and meets regularly with U.S. Government oversight agencies to provide feedback on that compliance. Our long history of successful compliance with the SSA allows BAE Systems to supply products and services to the Department of Defense, Intelligence Community and Homeland Security on some of the Nations most sensitive programs.
